Clea: There are many things that I need to report.
dobby_dispchara clear

Clea: Father, Mother... I apologize for not being able to
come here for so long.

Clea: When I come to this place, I feel like the two of them
have truly died inside me.

Clea: I have been thinking about who I really am for a long
time.

Clea: The answer is probably... when I defeated the dragon,
I believe.

Clea: And as I fulfill the dreams of my dear friends, I have
come to see what I should do, what I want to do.
Clea: I think people call that kind of thing a dream.

Clea: I will return this courage I borrowed from you,
Father, and this kindness I borrowed from you, Mother.

Clea: I'm alright now. During my long journey, I was able to
find my own courage and kindness.

Beloved daughter Clea: I am a daughter who has been showered
with a lot of love from both of you.
Village Girl Clea: I am a village girl from Arche Village.

Adventurer Clea: I am an adventurer who protects freedom at
the Adventurer Guild, Ftera.

Clea: Who am I... I have decided that I can be both a
daughter and an adventurer.

Clea: People are free to choose multiple ways of being,
there is no contradiction in that.

Clea: I couldn't accept such a simple thing. This
stubbornness and clumsiness might be inherited from Father.

Clea: Father, Mother... You don't have to worry anymore,
Clea is alright.

Clea: I'm sorry for causing you worry. Thank you for loving
me more than anything.
Clea: Goodbye, Father, Mother.

Clea: I will come back to talk about the adventures at the
Adventurer Guild, stories from my journey, and most
importantly, about my friends--

Thief Nora: I think it's this way! I can smell a slightly
sweet scent of Clea-san!

Mage Relm: That's a really useful nose... I know, if I could
reproduce that with magic, it would be so convenient!

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, in that case, I would be found
immediately by the scent of wine.
Clea: Can you hear it? The voices of my dear friends.
Clea: Father, Mother.
Clea: I'm off--
イベント終了用
